==English==

===Etymology===
"Los angelization" gets its name from the post-[[World War II]] growth of the '''City of [[Los Angeles]], [[California]]''' located in [[w:Southern California|Southern California]] in the western [[United States]]. The city is the [[county seat]] of [[w:Los Angeles County, California|Los Angeles County]].

===Alternative spellings===
'''losangelization'''

===Noun===
'''Los Angelization'''

# {{slang}} Disperse [[w:urban development]]; [[urban sprawl]].

